# # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # #   2. TH├ŖM long_range_aux_loss() chß╗ē cho step 8-12 (48h-72h), zero risk cho 6-24h
# # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # #   3. Phase weight cho long_range loss: chß╗ē bß║Łt sau epoch 20 (sau khi 12h ß╗Ģn)
