# # # # # # # # # # # # # Step weights: nhß║źn mß║Īnh 48h (step 8) v├Ā 72h (step 12)
# # # # # # # # # # # # # 6h  12h  18h  24h  30h  36h  42h  48h  54h  60h  66h  72h
