# # # # # # # # # # ROOT CAUSE ANALYSIS tß╗½ v41/v45 plateau ß╗¤ 384km:
# # # # # # # # # #   - Loss qu├Ī phß╗®c tß║Īp: 6+ terms, conflicting gradients
# # # # # # # # # #   - FNO auxiliary loss, speed_acc, decomp,... ŌåÆ gradient war
# # # # # # # # # #   - Model hß╗Źc "average" thay v├¼ trajectory structure

# # # # # # # # # # INSIGHT tß╗½ ST-Trans (297km, 394k params):
# # # # # # # # # #   - Loss Cß╗░C ─ÉŲĀN GIß║óN: DPE + 0.05*MSE + speed_penalty + accel_penalty
# # # # # # # # # #   - Kh├┤ng c├│ AFCRPS, kh├┤ng c├│ ATE/CTE decomp, kh├┤ng c├│ FNO aux
# # # # # # # # # #   - Physics = chß╗ē penalty over-speed v├Ā jerk, kh├┤ng enforce dynamics
# # # # # # # # # #   - Non-autoregressive: predict all steps parallel

# # # # # # # # # # v46 STRATEGY ŌĆö "ST-Trans loss, FM architecture":
# # # # # # # # # #   LOSS = haversine_DPE (weighted) + 0.05*coord_MSE + ╬╗_spd*speed_penalty + ╬╗_acc*accel_penalty

# # # # # # # # # #   Key fix: speed_penalty d├╣ng DATA-DRIVEN threshold tß╗½ obs_traj
# # # # # # # # # #     - Tß╗½ data thß╗▒c: TC speed ~ 5-19 km/h (6h step)
# # # # # # # # # #     - vmax_kmh c┼® = 80 ŌåÆ KH├öNG BAO GIß╗£ trigger
# # # # # # # # # #     - Mß╗øi: compute_speed_stats_from_norm() ŌåÆ v_opt, v_sigma, v_hard_cap tß╗½ data

# # # # # # # # # #   ─ÉŲĪn giß║Żn h├│a ho├Ān to├Ān:
# # # # # # # # # #   - Bß╗Ä: FNO aux loss, speed_acc term, decomp, cons, FM_MSE balance
# # # # # # # # # #   - GIß╗«: haversine accuracy + kinematic regularization (nhŲ░ ST-Trans)
# # # # # # # # # #   - TH├ŖM: step weights nhß║źn mß║Īnh 48h/72h, adaptive speed threshold

# # # # # # # # # #   ─Éiß╗üu chß╗ēnh sigma schedule:
# # # # # # # # # #   - Epoch 0-10: sigma=0.15 (near-deterministic, hß╗Źc fast)
# # # # # # # # # #   - Epoch 10-40: linear decay 0.15ŌåÆ0.03
# # # # # # # # # #   - Epoch 40+: sigma=0.03 (full FM diversity)

