# # # # # # # # #     ŌåÆ Giß╗Ø inject trß╗▒c tiß║┐p v├Āo transformer decoder memory
# # # # # # # # #     ŌåÆ Decoder biß║┐t TC ─æang ─æi hŲ░ß╗øng n├Āo theo env data

