# # # # # # # # #     ŌåÆ Giß║Żm l_speed tß╗½ 0.1ŌåÆ0.05 v├¼ l_speed_match thay thß║┐

# # # # # # # # #   [FIX-5] STEP_WEIGHTS: t─āng trß╗Źng sß╗æ 12h/24h
# # # # # # # # #     ŌåÆ Penalize sai tß╗æc ─æß╗Ö sß╗øm ŌåÆ tr├Īnh error accumulation

# # # # # # # # #   [FIX-6] sample(): init tß╗½ persistence forecast thay v├¼ pure noise
# # # # # # # # #     ŌåÆ Ensemble members bß║»t ─æß║¦u tß╗½ "TC ─æi thß║│ng" ŌåÆ physically reasonable

# # # # # # # # #   [FIX-7] Tß║»t _physics_correct (g├óy shrinkage trajectory)

