# # # # # # FIXES vs v53 (ATE plateau breakthrough ŌĆö 5 fixes):

# # # # # # DIAGNOSIS tß╗½ 100 epoch training log:
# # # # # #   ATE bß╗ŗ STUCK ß╗¤ ~144km tß╗½ ep30 ŌåÆ ep99 (zero progress)
# # # # # #   CTE tiß║┐p tß╗źc giß║Żm: 322ŌåÆ54km (excellent)
# # # # # #   fm_mse T─éNG ep10ŌåÆep99: 1.5ŌåÆ7.0 (anomaly ŌĆö catastrophic forgetting)
# # # # # #   ATE:CTE ratio = 2.7:1 ŌåÆ speed error, kh├┤ng phß║Żi direction error

# # # # # # ROOT CAUSE: fm_mse t─āng ŌåÆ flow predictions = NOISE ŌåÆ ensemble average
# # # # # #   = persistence forecast ŌåÆ persistence underestimates TC acceleration
# # # # # #   ŌåÆ ATE stuck tß║Īi persistence error level (~144km cho SCS TCs)

# # # # # #   [FIX-ATE-1] fm_mse ├Ś 1.0 ŌåÆ ├Ś 4.0 (stop flow forgetting)
# # # # # #     v53: total = l_fm_mse ├Ś 1.0 + 2.0 ├Ś loss_dict["total"]
# # # # # #     v54: total = l_fm_mse ├Ś 4.0 + 2.0 ├Ś loss_dict["total"]
# # # # # #     Tß║Īi sao: fm_mse ─æang t─āng ŌåÆ velocity predictions = noise
# # # # # #     ŌåÆ 50-member ensemble averages to persistence forecast
# # # # # #     ŌåÆ persistence underestimates TC speed ŌåÆ ATE stuck at ~144km
# # # # # #     Expected: fm_mse < 1.0 trong 10 epochs ŌåÆ clean velocity predictions

# # # # # #   [FIX-ATE-2] Loss rebalance: t─āng ATE budget, giß║Żm CTE budget
# # # # # #     v53: signed_ate├Ś0.40  signed_cte├Ś0.25  heading├Ś0.20
# # # # # #     v54: signed_ate├Ś0.80  signed_cte├Ś0.08  heading├Ś0.08
# # # # # #     Tß║Īi sao: CTE=54km ─æ├Ż beat target 93.58 bß║▒ng 40km ŌåÆ dŲ░ gradient
# # # # # #     ŌåÆ Chuyß╗ān gradient budget sang ATE
# # # # # #     ŌåÆ signed_cte kh├┤ng bß╗ŗ x├│a ho├Ān to├Ān (vß║½n giß╗» 0.08 ─æß╗ā CTE stable)
# # # # # #     ŌåÆ heading giß║Żm (CTE supervision ─æ├Ż ─æß╗¦)

# # # # # #   [FIX-ATE-3] Adaptive CTE-to-ATE budget shift (epoch-based)
# # # # # #     Khi epoch Ōēź 30 (CTE ─æ├Ż converge): tß╗▒ ─æß╗Öng t─āng ATE pressure
# # # # # #     signed_ate weight: 0.80 ŌåÆ 0.80 + 0.02├Ś(ep-30)/10, capped at 1.2
# # # # # #     signed_cte weight: 0.08 ŌåÆ 0.08 ├Ś decay (giß║Żm dß║¦n khi CTE ß╗Ģn ─æß╗ŗnh)
# # # # # #     Tß║Īi sao: kh├┤ng hard-code epoch, d├╣ng relative schedule

# # # # # #   [FIX-ATE-4] _persistence_blend = 0.0 tß║Īi inference (x├│a ho├Ān to├Ān)
# # # # # #     v53: blend_strength=0.20
# # # # # #     v54: blend_strength=0.00
# # # # # #     Tß║Īi sao: persistence underestimates TC acceleration ŌåÆ ATE positive bias
# # # # # #     CTE ─æ├Ż tß╗æt ŌåÆ kh├┤ng cß║¦n persistence ─æß╗ā stabilize direction

# # # # # #   [FIX-ATE-5] vel_reg ├Ś 0.60 ŌåÆ ├Ś 1.20 + add speed_bias_loss
# # # # # #     vel_reg weight: 0.60 ŌåÆ 1.20 (double)
# # # # # #     + th├¬m _speed_bias_loss(): penalize dŲ░ß╗øi-estimate speed ─æß║Ęc biß╗ćt
# # # # # #       SCS TCs thŲ░ß╗Øng accelerate ŌåÆ under-predict = systematic error
# # # # # #     Tß║Īi sao: vel_reg ß╗¤ ep30+ Ōēł 0.01-0.08 (qu├Ī nhß╗Å) ŌåÆ speed supervision
# # # # # #     ─æ├Ż "converge" sai (train distribution bias)

# # # # # # Kept from v53:
# # # # # #   [FIX-B] heading km-space correction (cos_lat)
# # # # # #   [FIX-C] OT matching x0ŌåÆx1
# # # # # #   [FIX-D] steering_enc Linear(7,64)
# # # # # #   [FIX-P1-A] signed_ate km-space
# # # # # #   [FIX-P2-B] signed_cte mirror
# # # # # #   [FIX-P1-B] vel_reg no ratio, clamp 5.0
# # # # # #   [FIX-P2-A] sph_ate_cte ate_w=2.0,cte_w=2.5
