# # #     ŌåÆ Chuyß╗ān gradient budget sang ATE
# # #     ŌåÆ signed_cte kh├┤ng bß╗ŗ x├│a ho├Ān to├Ān (vß║½n giß╗» 0.08 ─æß╗ā CTE stable)
# # #     ŌåÆ heading giß║Żm (CTE supervision ─æ├Ż ─æß╗¦)

# # #   [FIX-ATE-3] Adaptive CTE-to-ATE budget shift (epoch-based)
