# V62: AR-SEEDED FLOW MATCHING (AR-FM)
# ŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆ
# ROOT CAUSE cß╗¦a 130-145km floor:
#   Standard FM: x0 = N(0,Žā┬▓) ŌåÆ x1 = GT  (transport d├Āi, regression-to-mean)
#   Encoder nhß║Łn gradient pha trß╗Ön FM+ATE ŌåÆ kh├┤ng optimize thuß║¦n ATE

# V62 Fix ŌĆö 2 thay ─æß╗Ģi kiß║┐n tr├║c:

# [v62-1] GRU Autoregressive Head (thay direct_head MLP):
#   ctx_ar ŌåÆ GRU(2 layers, autoregressive) ŌåÆ positions(12 steps)
#   Loss: haversine(AR_pred, GT) ├Ś STEP_WEIGHTS
#   Gradient: 100% THUß║”N ATE ŌåÆ encoder (GIß╗ÉNG LSTM baseline)
#   Teacher forcing: 70%ŌåÆ30% theo epoch
#   Encoder train EXACTLY nhŲ░ LSTM vß╗ü gradient quality.

# [v62-2] AR-Seeded FM Source Distribution:
#   Standard FM: x0 = N(0,Žā┬▓)         transport = ŌĆ¢GT - N(0,1)ŌĆ¢  (d├Āi)
#   AR-FM:       x0 = AR_pred + Žā╬Ą    transport = ŌĆ¢GT - AR_predŌĆ¢  (ngß║»n!)
#   FM chß╗ē hß╗Źc RESIDUAL: u = GT - x0_ar
  
#   ŌåÆ FM velocity field dß╗ģ hß╗Źc hŲĪn (shorter transport)
#   ŌåÆ Diversity: Žā_ar=0.30 ŌåÆ FM ensemble diverse xung quanh AR
#   ŌåÆ AR sai ŌåÆ residual lß╗øn ŌåÆ FM c├│ room ─æß╗ā correct

# [v62-3] Gradient Isolation:
#   raw_ctx ŌöĆŌöĆŌåÆ ctx_fc2_ar ŌåÆ GRU head ŌåÆ haversine  ŌåÉ 100% ATE encoder grad
#             ŌööŌöĆŌöĆŌåÆ .detach() ŌåÆ FM path             ŌåÉ FM gradient KH├öNG vß╗ü encoder

# Inference:
#   AR_pred = ar_head(ctx_ar)           # base prediction (clean)
#   FM samples = DDIM(x0=AR_pred+Žā╬Ą)   # diverse refinements
#   pred = FM sample gß║¦n AR_pred nhß║źt  # best of both worlds

# Literature:
#   GenCast (Google 2023): diffusion tr├¬n residual vs NWP (external, kh├┤ng jointly trained)
#   AR-FM: jointly trained GRU + gradient isolation ŌåÆ NOVEL cho TC forecasting

# Expected:
#   ep20: ar_ate ~120km  (ngang LSTM ep20)
#   ep35: ar_ate ~95km   (beat LSTM baseline)
#   ep50: val_ATE ~85-95km (beat STraNs target 79.94km khß║Ż thi)
#   CTE:  FM diversity + clean AR ŌåÆ ~80-90km

# V59 CORE CHANGES ŌĆö Ph├Ī vß╗Ī ngŲ░ß╗Īng 130-145km:

#   ROOT CAUSE of 130-145km floor:
#     FM hß╗Źc p(trajectory|context) ŌĆö distribution modeling
#     ATE ─æo point estimate ŌĆö 1 trajectory
#     MEAN cß╗¦a 50 samples ŌåÆ regression-to-mean ŌåÆ systematic ATE bias
#     Fast TCs v├Ā slow TCs ─æß╗üu bß╗ŗ k├®o vß╗ü mean_speed ŌåÆ BIG ERROR

#   [v59-1] MBR (Minimum Bayes Risk) Decoding
#     TRŲ»ß╗ÜC: pred = mean(top_k_samples)   ŌåÉ regression-to-mean
#     SAU:   pred = argmin_i ╬Ż_j ATE(s_i, s_j)  ŌåÉ central sample
#     L├Į thuyß║┐t: E[ATE(mean,gt)] Ōēź E[ATE(MBR,gt)]  (Jensen)
#     Kh├┤ng cß║¦n retrain ŌĆö test ngay vß╗øi checkpoint hiß╗ćn tß║Īi
#     Expected: -15 ─æß║┐n -30km ATE

#   [v59-2] Direct Regression Head
#     ctx(256) ŌåÆ Linear(512) ŌåÆ Linear(256) ŌåÆ Linear(24) ŌåÆ trajectory
#     Loss: haversine(pred_direct, gt) ├Ś STEP_WEIGHTS ├Ś 3.0
#     Inference: blend (1-w)├ŚMBR + w├Śdirect, w t─āng dß║¦n ep20ŌåÆ50ŌåÆ60%
#     Gradient trß╗▒c tiß║┐p tß╗½ ATE metric v├Āo weights
#     Expected: -20 ─æß║┐n -40km ATE th├¬m sau ep30+

#   Giß╗» FM: vß║½n d├╣ng FM cho direction diversity + uncertainty
#   Giß╗» speed_head: auxiliary supervision cho speed encoding
#   Bß╗Å: hybrid ensemble c┼® (replaced by MBR+direct)

#   Expected total: ATE ~90-120km @ ep50-70

# V58 ARCHITECTURE FIXES (root cause: fm_mse stuck at 1-2):

#   [FIX-ARCH-1] ctx h_t: Mamba(128) + FNO_global(128) = 256-dim
#     BEFORE: h_t = Mamba(obs_traj) = 128-dim (tiny)
#     AFTER:  h_t = cat[Mamba(128), e_3d_global(128)] = 256-dim
#     WHY: Context lacked ERA5 spatial structure ŌåÆ fm_mse stuck
#     ctx_fc1 updated: Linear(176ŌåÆ304, 512)

#   [FIX-ARCH-1b] decoder_proj: Linear(1ŌåÆ128, 16)
#     BEFORE: f_sp = weighted_sum(e_3d_dec) ŌåÆ 1 scalar ŌåÆ Linear(1,16)
#     AFTER:  f_sp = mean(e_3d_bot spatial) ŌåÆ 128-dim ŌåÆ Linear(128,16)
#     WHY: "Spatial decoder" was 1 number ŌåÆ useless for conditioning

#   [FIX-ARCH-4] Sample selection: speed-anchored correction
#     BEFORE: median of top-35% samples (may still be too slow)
#     AFTER:  + speed anchor: if pred_speed < obs_speed ŌåÆ stretch by ratio
#     WHY: Systematic under-prediction in ATE

#   [FIX-ARCH-5] Speed regression head: ctx(256) ŌåÆ speed_head ŌåÆ 12 steps
#     Auxiliary loss: MSE(pred_speed_normalized, gt_speed/20) ├Ś 3.0
#     WHY: Forces ctx representation to encode TC speed ŌåÆ fm_mse improves

#   [FIX-ARCH-6] Transformer depth 2ŌåÆ4 layers
#     6 memory slots need Ōēź3 layers for proper integration
#     +2 layers add ~2.1M params

#   EXPECTED: fm_mse < 1.0 @ ep5, < 0.5 @ ep15, ATE < 120km @ ep20

#   [FIX-v58-4] QUAN TRß╗īNG ŌĆö Train script: d├╣ng ATE ─æß╗ā select checkpoint!
#     Val_loss KH├öNG c├│ correlation vß╗øi ATE (log evidence: vlossŌåō ATEŌåæ ß╗¤ ep10-30)
#     Sß╗Ła trong train script:
#       save_best_condition = (val_ATE < best_ATE)  # NOT val_loss!

#   [FIX-v58-1] Curriculum removed: always train full 12 steps
#     Curriculum g├óy 72h error t─āng (527ŌåÆ625km) = negative transfer

#   [FIX-v58-3] fm_mse progressive: w_fm = min(12, 6 + 0.2*(ep-20))
#     Chß╗æng catastrophic forgetting (fm_mse t─āng ep10ŌåÆ90)

#   [FIX-v58-5] Dropout 0.10ŌåÆ0.15 ─æß╗ā giß║Żm valŌåÆtest gap (+105km)

#   [FIX-v58-6] Speed augmentation: scale traj speed Ōłł [0.7, 1.4]
#     Gi├║p model generalize to faster/slower storms

# MONITOR:
#   fm_mse phß║Żi GIß║óM: ep0=1-2, ep10<1.0, ep20<0.5
#   ATE_km phß║Żi GIß║óM li├¬n tß╗źc: ep10<120, ep20<100, ep30<80
#   CTE_km KH├öNG t─āng qu├Ī 70km (vß║½n dŲ░ß╗øi target 93.58)
